description: I wanted to try to pick up a guy on a bus, just to spice things up. And I got two! They wanted to go jogging. So I invited myself to go with them. I was a bit intrusive but they didn´t mind it that much. One of the boys had a bad back so I suggested that his friend should give him a massage. They laughed at me. Then I offered them money... It took a few minutes but I managed to talk them into it. What started with a massage turned into crazy and serious stuff. I didn´t expect the guys would have the balls for it. I made them to do very nasty things to each other while people were walking by the trees we were hiding behind. When I joined them, we had to be very careful. The boys moaned so loud we almost got caught. I doubt they went jogging after I was gone.
title: Czech Hunter 312
